few-shot.example:
Convert these sentences to JSON with sentiment analysis:

Input: "I love this product!"
Output: {"text": "I love this product!", "sentiment": "positive", "score": 0.95}

Input: "It doesn't work at all."
Output: {"text": "It doesn't work at all.", "sentiment": "negative", "score": 0.88}

Now analyze: "Fantastic experience, I recommend it!"
